Maintainer: Sayani Gupta <gupta.sayani@gmail.com>
Description: Provides tools for exploring large quantities of temporal data 
             across different deconstructions of time.
             Computes circular, aperiodic, single-order-up or 
             multiple-order-up granularities and advices on which
             combinations of granularities to explore and through which 
             distribution plots.
